channel.title: Somthing wrong with toms cache editer?
channel.description:
Ok so i was editing my cache and went and played some ps3. I then came back and my mom closed my cache editer so i opened it again. i loaded ym cache but when i tryed and edit anything it doesnt work
Picture:I have pressed ok like 5 times and nothing happens.... [img]http://img104.imageshack.us/img104/7318/gfcatchediter.jpg[/img]
If any one knows how to fix this please tell me :)
